parsed_range = Range.parse(value)
assert parsed_range == expected_range
pytest.mark.parametrize('value,expected_range', [(b'bytes=100-', Range(
    'bytes', [RangePart(100, None)])), (b'bytes=-120', Range('bytes', [
    RangePart(None, 120)])), ('bytes=-120', Range('bytes', [RangePart(None,
    120)])), ('bytes=100-200, 400-600, 300-500', Range('bytes', [RangePart(
    100, 200), RangePart(400, 600), RangePart(300, 500)])), (
    'bytes=100-200,400-600,300-500', Range('bytes', [RangePart(100, 200),
    RangePart(400, 600), RangePart(300, 500)])), ('bytes=1200-, -100',
    Range('bytes', [RangePart(1200, None), RangePart(None, 100)]))])
